    17вҶ’## Pull Request Conventions вҖҰ
    19вҶ’### Commits
    21вҶ’We use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/).
    22вҶ’
    23вҶ’When opening a pull request please be sure that either the pull request title, or each commit in the pull request, has one of the following prefixes:
    24вҶ’
    25вҶ’ - `feat`: For when introducing a new feature.  The result will be a new semver minor version of the package when it is next published.
    26вҶ’ - `fix`: For bug fixes. The result will be a new semver patch version of the package when it is next published.
    27вҶ’ - `docs`: For documentation updates.  The result will be a new semver patch version of the package when it is next published.
      вҶ’вҖҰ
