    10вҶ’## Usage
    12вҶ’Consider an INI file such as the following:
    13вҶ’
    14вҶ’```ini
    15вҶ’; This comment is being ignored
    16вҶ’scope = global
    17вҶ’
    18вҶ’[database]
    19вҶ’user = dbuser
    20вҶ’password = dbpassword
    21вҶ’database = use_this_database
    22вҶ’
    23вҶ’[paths.default]
    24вҶ’datadir = /var/lib/data
    25вҶ’array[] = first value
    26вҶ’array[] = second value
    27вҶ’array[] = third value
    28вҶ’```
    29вҶ’
