   103вҶ’     * 
   104вҶ’     *  Disabled by default to have better 
   105вҶ’     *  compatibility with old picky parsers.
   106вҶ’     */
   107вҶ’
   108вҶ’    whitespace : false ,
   109вҶ’
   110вҶ’    /**
   111вҶ’     *  Whether to align the `=` character for each section.
   112вҶ’     *  -> Also enables the `whitespace` option
      вҶ’вҖҰ
   167вҶ’### Un / Escape
   169вҶ’Turn the given string into a safe to  
   170вҶ’use key or value in your INI file.
   171вҶ’
   172вҶ’```js
   173вҶ’safe(`"unsafe string"`) // -> \"unsafe string\"
   174вҶ’```
   175вҶ’
   176вҶ’Or reverse the process with:
   177вҶ’
   178вҶ’```js
   179вҶ’unsafe(`\\"safe string\\"`) // -> "safe string"
   180вҶ’```
